data.description: Come admire this lush pink home in the heart of Home Seekers Paradise. Stroll through the freshly painted petite iron gates, as you make your way back into the 1900's with an updated farmhouse/modern feel. Upon entering take note of the french doors, corbels and transoms. All 2500+/- sq ft of this home has been well loved and very much admired. If walls could talk I can only imagine the stories it would tell. 3 oversized bedrooms on the lower level including the master, with an additional 2 bedrooms upstairs AND a bonus room/office space. This spacious floor plan allows for an abundance of natural light, an updated galley style kitchen with two-toned cabinetry, mix of marble, brick and stained wood. New lighting creates a cozy ambiance & the beautiful built ins are all the rage. Be sure to stop at the top of the stairs & for a quick peek through the picture window. If this home at first glance doesn't give you the doll house feel, the upper level surely will. Though situated inside the city limits a privacy fence encompasses the back yard creating a great space for entertaining. Small covered 1 car carport provides parking out of the element. Schedule your private viewing today. Storm Shelter does NOT remain with the property. Bank letter required for all showings.
